OL,5,G0100 #Text Me When You Get Home
OL,6,     FIn 2014, estate agent Beverly
OL,7,     FCarter was kidnapped and killed
OL,8,     Fwhile showing a home to a person
OL,9,     Fshe believed was a potential
OL,10,     Fbuyer. Detectives used phone data
OL,11,     Fto help find her body.
OL,12,G0155 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FA butcher from Somerset brings a
OL,14,     Fmeaty lipoma on his neck for Dr
OL,15,     FDev Shah. Dr Toby Nelson has a
OL,16,     Fpatient with a skin condition
OL,17,     Faround her eyes.
